tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE certifications_earned (
    athlete_id UUID,
    certification_name VARCHAR(50),
    certification_date DATE,
    expiration_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY (athlete_id, certification_name)
);

CREATE TABLE competitions_won (
    athlete_id INT,
    competition_name VARCHAR(50),
    competition_date DATE,
    winning_position INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (athlete_id) REFERENCES personal_records(athlete_id)
);

CREATE TABLE certifications_earned (
    athlete_id INT,
    certification_name VARCHAR(50),
    certification_date DATE,
    issuing_organization VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (athlete_id) REFERENCES personal_records(athlete_id)
);

CREATE TABLE athletes (
    athlete_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    athlete_name VARCHAR(50),
    date_of_birth DATE,
    height FLOAT,
    weight FLOAT
);
